# ==============================================================================
# NOTES
# ==============================================================================
# 
# - Code owners are automatically requested for review when a PR changes their files
# - At least one code owner must approve before a PR can be merged (if enabled in branch protection)
# - The last matching pattern has precedence
# - Use teams for larger projects: @org/team-name
# - Regular contributors can be added as they earn trust
# 
# Learn more: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
